title: Michael Cheika on a mission to restore the faith in Wallabies
text:
Michael Cheika on a mission to restor... Michael Cheika on a mission to restore the faith in Wallabies Next Story Prev Story 2 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
The big freeze had found its way to Brisbane just as Michael Cheika embarks on the big sell for a code that desperately needs to turn up the heat. On Saturday night, a for the first time, the Cheika-coached Wallabies will be beamed around the nation in prime time and the new coach remains determined to leave an impression, regardless of the result against the visiting Springboks.   The Age.
